<div class="container search">
  <div class="divider"></div>
  <div class="section">
    <h5 id="search-header">Search our Database, Get Real Numbers</h5>
    <div class="row">
      <div class="col s12 m12">
        <div class="card-panel">
        <span>How it works:<br> Select a year, institution, program and ethnicity from the menu below.<br>
          In return you receive four data metrics that you'll find valuable, which are:
            <ul>
              <li>The total number of graduates for your chosen program.</li>
              <li>The total number of graduates for your chosen ethnicity and program.</li>
              <li>A comparison of graduates of your chosen ethnicity against the rest of the program</li>
              <li>A comparison of graduates of your chosen ethnicity and program against all graduates of your chosen ethnicty of that institution.</li> 
            </ul>
        </span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  </div>
  <div class="form ">
  <%= form_tag :results, method: :get do %>
      <%= select_tag 'year', options_from_collection_for_select(years, :date_year, :date_year), prompt: "Select Year", class:"browser-default"%>
      <%= select_tag 'college', options_for_select([]), prompt: "Select Institution", class:"browser-default"%>
      <%= select_tag 'program', options_for_select([]), prompt: "Select Program", class:"browser-default"%>
      <%= select_tag 'ethnicity', options_from_collection_for_select(ethnicities,:ethnicity, :ethnicity), prompt: "Select Ethnicity", class:"browser-default"%>
      <%= submit_tag "Get Results"%>
    <% end %>
  </div>
</div>
 